    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-115_122944_000063_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/115/122944/115_122944_000063_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-115",
        "content": "Even concubinage has been corrupted-by marriage.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-115_122944_000090_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/115/122944/115_122944_000090_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-115",
        "content": "Around the hero everything becomes a tragedy; around the demigod everything becomes a satyr play; and around God everything becomes-what? perhaps a \"world\"?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-115_122944_000093_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/115/122944/115_122944_000093_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-115",
        "content": "What is done out of love always takes place beyond good and evil.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-115_122944_000094_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/115/122944/115_122944_000094_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-115",
        "content": "Objection, evasion, joyous distrust, and love of irony are signs of health; everything absolute belongs to pathology.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-115_122944_000096_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/115/122944/115_122944_000096_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-115",
        "content": "Insanity in individuals is something rare-but in groups, parties, nations, and epochs it is the rule.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-115_122944_000098_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/115/122944/115_122944_000098_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-115",
        "content": "Not only our reason, but also our conscience, truckles to our strongest impulse-the tyrant in us.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-115_122944_000106_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/115/122944/115_122944_000106_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-115",
        "content": "One may indeed lie with the mouth; but with the accompanying grimace one nevertheless tells the truth.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-115_122944_000107_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/115/122944/115_122944_000107_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-115",
        "content": "To vigorous men intimacy is a matter of shame-and something precious.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-115_122944_000111_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/115/122944/115_122944_000111_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-115",
        "content": "Pity has an almost ludicrous effect on a man of knowledge, like tender hands on a Cyclops.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-115_122944_000112_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/115/122944/115_122944_000112_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-115",
        "content": "One occasionally embraces some one or other, out of love to mankind (because one cannot embrace all); but this is what one must never confess to the individual.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
]